 and investing in technology companies he previously served as ceo of warner music group from  to  and as chairman of warner music group from  to  in may  the sale of wmg was announced bronfman would continue as ceo in the transaction in august  he became chairman of the company as stephen cooper became ceo bronfman previously served as ceo of seagram and vicechairman of vivendi universal bronfman jr expanded and later divested ownership of the seagram company and also worked as a broadway and film producer and songwriter under the pseudonyms junior miles and sam roman contents  early life  business career  film producing  seagram company  warner music group  music career  personal life  insider trading conviction  stance on music copyright infringement  references  further reading  external links early lifeedit born in citation needed edgar jr efer to friends is the son of edgar miles bronfman and the grandson of samuel bronfman patriarch of one of the wealthiest and most influential jewish families in canadacitation needed the bronfman family gained its fortunes through the seagram company an alcohol distilling company edgar jr is the second of five children of ann loeb and edgar miles bronfman his mother was the daughter of john langeloth loeb sr a wall street investment banker whose company was a predecessor of shearson lehmanamerican express and frances lehman a scion of the lehman brothers banking firm they divorced in  he was particularly active in school theater an interest his parents supported by donating to construct the ann and edgar bronfman theatre during a  expansion at the collegiate school a private school in manhattan which edgar jr attended edgar jr and his classmates created a documentary film of the school that spawned the collegiate film festival an event that gained positive press in the los angeles times and the village voice in the summer before his junior year in high school bronfman went to london to work on a feature film arranged partly 