artnerships with its artists over that time wmg has grown from the fourthlargest to the thirdlargest music company in the world in  wmg achieved its highest us album market share in ten years and the company has had the no  label in the us four times since  in  bronfman presided over the sale of wmg to access industries a usbased industrial group for  billion bronfman also serves as general partner at accretive llc a venture capital firm specializing in the business process outsourcing area before assuming his current position at wmg bronfman served as chairman and ceo of lexa partners llc a management venture capital group based in new york city bronfman serves on the board accretive health he is chairman of the board of endeavor global a nonprofit organization pioneering a new approach to international development bronfman also serves on the boards of new york university elaine a and kenneth g langone medical center and the collegiate school and is a member of the council on foreign relations prev bio victor kaufman next bio chelsea clinton back all leadership overview leadership history iac cares news button scroll up leadership  iac skip to main content iac about overview leadership history iac cares news arrow     our brands apalon prevprev brand apalonnextnext brand apalon ask applications prevprev brand ask applicationsnextnext brand ask applications askcom prevprev brand askcomnextnext brand askcom citygrid prevprev brand citygridnextnext brand citygrid collegehumor prevprev brand collegehumornextnext brand collegehumor daily burn prevprev brand daily burnnextnext brand daily burn dictionarycom prevprev brand dictionarycomnextnext brand dictionarycom dotdash formerly aboutcom prevprev brand dotdash formerly aboutcomnextnext brand dotdash formerly aboutcom electus prevprev brand electusnextnext brand electus felix prevprev brand felixnextnext brand felix homeadvisor prevprev brand homeadvisornextnext brand homeadvisor investopedia prevprev brand investopedian